moveVariable

public boolean moveVariable(int gotoi,
                            java.lang.String varName)
moveVariable

Parameters:
gotoi - can be from 0 to the size of the variable list
varName - - name of variable to move
Returns:
worked - true if success false otherwise The way this works is that the goto index is as if we cloned the named variable, inserted it in the list at the specified location (thus the list would be the incoming size plus 1), and then deleted the original variable. Variables move down as others are inserted.
